{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was one kilogram.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was divided into four pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And each person got one quarter of that bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't think that anybody can visualize to divide such a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sometimes if these guards-- yeah, yeah, what I should say also was the administration of the camp itself was run by criminals.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Nazis had put criminals in charge of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those were German citizens, German people that were convicted of crimes for more than 10 years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had passed a law that any criminal that was convicted of a crime for more than 10 years would have to-- could not go back into society.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He has to serve out his time in a concentration camp-- I mean, after he had served the time of the prison term.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these criminals were the ones that were running the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were the block elders, like I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were the kapo that were in charge of the work detail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, those guys were criminals, hardened criminals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those guys left their frustration out on us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you can imagine what they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So sometimes what they would do, they would take such a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Would take one loaf of bread and say, here, four guys, you divide the bread into four portions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, can you imagine four hungry people that came back from a work detail where they worked all day digging ditches that are starved almost to death, give them a loaf of bread without a knife to divide that bread into four parts?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes that bread was moldy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the one person that got the moldy part would scream and yell that he cannot eat that part.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wants a good part of the bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
